Nigeria Won’t Convert Loans to Banks Into Equity, Thisday Says

-- B y   E m e l e   O n u
-- 
2011-06-11T10:26:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-11/nigeria-won-t-convert-loans-to-banks-into-equity-thisday-says.html
Nigeria won’t convert 620 bilion
naira ($4 billion) in emergency loans to eight rescued banks
into equity,  Thisday  reported, citing an interview with the
central bank Governor Sanusi Lamido.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emele Onu in Lagos at   eonu1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin in Johannesburg at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 